	* gsldatahandle-mad.[hc]: libmad based mp3 datahandle implementation.

	* gslloader-mad.c: gsldatahandle-mad.[hc] based mp3 loader.

	* gslcommon.[hc]: introduce new debugging mechanism and rework
	GSL messages.

