	functionality.

	* bsequery.c: quickly added facility to iterate over the
	fundamental types.

	* bseplugin.c (bse_plugin_register_types): register enums and flags
	types inline.

	* *.[hc]: port over to G_TYPE_ENUM and G_TYPE_FLAGS.

