	* bseglobals.h (BSE_MAX_NOTE): changed this to 123=dis+7=19912.127Hz,
	so we stay below BSE_MAX_OSC_FREQ_d (and below 22050).
	added BSE_MAX_OSC_FREQ_d=20000 and BSE_MIN_OSC_FREQ_d=1/20000.

